name: Ignacio Mosca personal page
body:
### Hi There!
My name is Ignacio. I'm a Backend Developer with 5+ years of experience in the industry.
My Experience goes from mission-critical applications for the Government as a contractor to payment processors. My Interests are Distributed Systems, Parallel Programming and Functional Languages on the JVM (For the past few years I've been learning Scala).
